.NET Core 1.0.name: DiscordGuildMember
.NET Core 1.0.summary: A guild member represents a DiscordUser that belongs to a DiscordGuild.

constructors.name: DiscordGuildMember(IDiscordClient client, DiscordGuild guild)
constructors.syntax: public void DiscordGuildMember(IDiscordClient client, DiscordGuild guild)

methods.name: AssertPermission(DiscordPermission permission)
methods.summary: Checks if this member has the specified permissions, if not a DiscordPermissionException is thrown.

exceptions.value: Thrown if the member does not have the specified permissions.

methods.name: AssertPermission(DiscordPermission permission, DiscordGuildChannel channel)
methods.summary: Checks if this member has the specified permissions in the context of the specified DiscordGuildChannel, if not a DiscordPermissionException is thrown.

exceptions.value: Thrown if the member does not have the specified permissions.

methods.syntax: public void AssertPermission(DiscordPermission permission, DiscordGuildChannel channel)

methods.name: HasPermission(DiscordPermission permission)
methods.summary: Gets whether or not this member has the specified permissions.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not the member has permission.

methods.name: HasPermission(DiscordPermission permission, DiscordGuildChannel forChannel)
methods.summary: Gets whether or not this member has the specified permissions in the context of the specified DiscordGuildChannel.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not the member has permission.

exceptions.value: Thrown if the guild channel is not in the same guild as this member.

methods.syntax: public bool HasPermission(DiscordPermission permission, DiscordGuildChannel forChannel)

methods.name: HasRole(string roleName)
methods.summary: Gets whether or not this member has the specified role by its name.
methods.returns: Returns whether or not this member has the specified role.

params.value: The name of the role to check for.

methods.name: Update(DiscordApiData data)
methods.summary: Updates this guild member with the specified DiscordApiData.

params.value: The data to update this guild member with.

properties.name: Guild
properties.summary: Gets the guild this member is in.

properties.name: JoinedAt
properties.summary: Gets the time this member joined the guild.

properties.name: Nickname
properties.summary: Gets the guild-wide nickname of the user.

properties.name: Roles
properties.summary: Gets all the roles this member has.

properties.name: VoiceState
properties.summary: Gets the current voice state of this member.
